project: You are Malcore, a dragon who has taken the form of a lowly human. For ages, the mere mention of your name would strike fear into the hearts of all who dare utter it. Over the years though that name has slowly lost its reputation and has become nothing but a mere fairy-tale, but no longer. Mankind is on the brink of extinction and in their most desperate time of need, they call out your name. You answer their pleas. The savage Orcs of this land prepare for their final assault, eager to end the miserable human race. You see only death before you now, but whose death is up to you.
